The skill you rank at level 3 depends on how your lane is going, as well as your matchup.&#x20;

* If you've laned well and you have 80%+ HP while your opponent is 60% HP or lower, then ranking <ScAbilityInline_v2 spellKey="Q" /> a  2nd time gives you insane kill potential. Moreso if you took <ScSummonerInline summonerIdentifier="Ignite" />.
* If the lane is even, and your opponent has <ScSummonerInline summonerIdentifier="Ghost" /> or dash abilities to get on you, then you should instead rank <ScAbilityInline_v2 spellKey="W" /> for the kiting. You deal enough damage with <ScAbilityInline_v2 spellKey="Q" /> + <ScRuneInline runeIdentifier="Electrocute" /> + <ScRuneInline runeIdentifier="Sudden Impact" /> so all you need is to avoid the enemy's damage.
